Description:
You reach the elevator leading to the next floor of the dwarven city, but it is stopped on the floor above you.

You try to call it up using a small lever, but unfortunately, it doesn't work.

After examining the lever, you realize that the mechanism is missing a small gear, and without it there is no way to bring it down from the floor above.
DescriptionAction: Your only chance to get to the next floor is to climb up the elevator chain.
